description_html:
Cate is a fresh concept for the cocktail table, which provides the ultimate in flexibility. These multi-tasking tables can be arranged in different configurations and provide various storage options. The Cate tables are perfect for many arrangements and are easy to move in front of a sleep sofa.
Features
• Wood tables with three unique design options
• Variations include door for storage, shelves and open ends
• Personalized finish options on wood
• Standard mirror top also available with Artisan Mirror options
product_name: Cate Clustered Cocktail Tables by Barry Goralnick for Vanguard Furniture
